The beginning of the anxiety of finding a way to archive some of my rhyme works and the confusion of finding a suitable medium to present them. Until in the process of searching for this medium, I was finally met at the point where I had to look again at the medium and the methods that I had found. Until finally I decided to present my rhyme work with digital media. Take advantage of smartphones and free applications for the process of making works. This work will also be distributed digitally, one of which is to respond to the current digital platform phenomenon, namely the NFT platform
